window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>He held the fate of two worlds in his hands.... </p> <p>Once he was an orphan called Pug, apprenticed to a sorcerer of the enchanted land of Midkemia. Then he was captured and enslaved by the Tsurani, a strange, warlike race of invaders from another world. </p> <p>There, in the exotic Empire of Kelewan, he earned a new name - <i>Milamber</i>. He learned to tame the unimagined powers that lay within him. And he took his place in an ancient struggle against an evil Enemy older than time itself. </p>"; 
